&lt;p>You are living comfortably at your home. &lt;br>
You have inquisitiveness to know the world around &lt;br>
So you go out and travel as far places as you want to know.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>While on the journey you feel you have to eat to survive &lt;br>
But you need money to eat and pay for &lt;br>
your temporary stay at different hotels. &lt;br>
For that, you need to earn money. &lt;br>
You learn some useful arts and skills.&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>About Experience</title><link>https://dasarpai.github.io/wiaposts/about-experience/</link><pubDate>Wed, 03 Feb 2016 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>hari@dasarpai.com (Dr. Hari Thapliyaal)</author><guid>https://dasarpai.github.io/wiaposts/about-experience/</guid><description>&lt;p>
